# core-ui

Modern.js 2 + React 18 + Tailwind + Radix (shadcn-style).

## Structure

- `src/routes/` — file-based pages (`page.tsx`, `layout.tsx`)
- `src/containers/` — feature UI blocks (may have `.stories.tsx`)
- `src/components/ui/` — reusable primitives (button, card, tabs, …)
- `src/hooks/api/{domain}/` — TanStack Query wrappers per API resource
- `src/hooks/url/` — URL param sync
- `src/lib/api-client.ts` — `initTsrReactQuery(contract, { baseUrl })`

## Data fetching pattern

```typescript
export const useFindLaunches = ({ pagination, filters, enabled }: Params) =>
  api.findLaunches.useQuery({
    queryKey: ["launches", pagination.offset, pagination.limit, filters.titleContains],
    queryData: { query: { offset, limit, "title~cnt": filters.titleContains } },
    enabled: enabled !== false,
  });
```

- Infer response types via `ClientInferResponseBody<typeof contract.findLaunches, 200>`.
- API base URL: `CORE_SERVICE_BASE_URL` env (default `http://localhost:3030`).
- Lint: Biome (`pnpm lint`). Stories: Storybook (`pnpm storybook`).
